  "projectName": "Ayush Synapse",
  "projectDescription": "A FHIR R4-compliant microservice that bridges NAMASTE (National AYUSH Morbidity and Standardized Terminologies Electronic) codes with ICD-11 TM2 and Biomedicine codes for interoperability with Indian EMR systems.",
